dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents bedrock contours for Waukesha County, Wisconsin in 2002. The dataset was originally published along with Technical Report No. 37: Groundwater Resources of Southeastern Wisconsin by the Southeastern Wisconsin Regional Planning Commission and the Wisconsin Geological and Natural History Survey in coorporation with the Wisconsin Department of Natural Resources in June 2002. This layer is part of the WaukeshaCounty_Groundwater_2002 collection.
